-- Fire Starts at PDVSA’s Cardon Refinery, El Universal Says
-- B y   N a t h a n   C r o o k s
-- 2012-02-06T05:39:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-06/fire-starts-at-pdvsa-s-cardon-refinery-el-universal-says.html
Petroleos de Venezuela SA had a
“considerable” fire at its Cardon refinery in Falcon state
yesterday, El Universal  reported , without saying where it
obtained the information.  The fire started at 8:30 p.m. local time at the refinery’s
CD-4 unit, and PDVSA, as the Caracas-based company is known, is
working to control the situation, the Venezuelan daily said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nathan Crooks in Caracas at 
 ncrooks@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at 
 dcrofts@bloomberg.net  